cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deploying AI-based services on mobile devices, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The concept of collaborative intelligence, where a part of the AI model runs on the mobile device and the rest in the cloud, is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also introduces a new loss function, which is a common topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
